Package: pez
Type: Package
Title: Phylogenetics for the Environmental Sciences
Version: 0.2
Date: 2013-11-15
Author: Matthew R. Helmus, William D. Pearse
Maintainer: Will Pearse <wdpearse@umn.edu>
Description: Eco-phylogenetic and community phylogenetic analyses.
    Keeps community ecological and phylogenetic data matched up and
    comparable using 'comparative.comm' objects. Wrappers for common
    community phylogenetic indices ('shape', 'evenness', 'dispersion', and
    'dissimilarity' metrics). Simplified and improved model-based
    approaches using Phylogenetic Generalised Linear Mixed Models (PGLMM).
License: GPL-2
